            "text": "Monsanto. contributed to pink bollworm resistance to the Cry1Ac protein in Bollgard I in Gujarat are limited refuge planting and early use of unapproved Bt cotton seed, Source: Wikipedia (en) URL: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monsanto",
