            "marker": "[3]",
            "title": "Crop Guide: Cotton (कापूस)",
            "text": "Crop: Cotton (कापूस). Scientific: Gossypium hirsutum. Season: Kharif. Ideal soil: Black Cotton Soil, Deep Clay Loam. Ideal temp: 21-35°C. Ideal rainfall: 500-1000 mm. Duration: 160 days. Stages: Sowing, Vegetative, Squaring, Flowering, Boll Formation, Harvesting. Major pests: Pink Bollworm, Aphids, Whitefly, Jassids. Major diseases: Bacterial Blight, Fungous Wilt, Leaf Curl. Source: ICAR-CICR open advisory.",
